    <title>Playa Luna | Beach, Restaurant & Events - Varcaturo, Naples</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Discover Playa Luna in Varcaturo: an exclusive experience featuring fine seafood dining, beach relaxation, and unforgettable sunset parties. Your luxury coastal retreat.">
    
